properties.SQL Query:
SELECT
    CAST(
    	if(
    		s.dt = '1970-01-01' or s.dt = today(),
    		today() - 30,    		
    		s.dt + INTERVAL 1 DAY
    	) AS String) AS dt,
    a.iata, 
    a.airport
FROM ya.airports a
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT 
        yairport,
        toDate(max(parseDateTime64BestEffort(date))) AS dt
    FROM ya.schedule 
    GROUP BY yairport
) s ON a.iata = s.yairport
ORDER BY a.iata;
